### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = 

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Registrar usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Registrar usuario admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "juan@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Obtener perfil (reemplaza el token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar usuarios (solo admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar usuarios con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}} 